@startuml
actor ユーザー as user
participant "SearchManager" as sm
participant "Thread" as th

== キーワード検索 ==
user -> sm: 検索(keyword)
sm -> sm: searchThreadTitle(keyword): Thread[]
sm -> th: スレッド取得(タイトル一致)
sm --> user: 検索結果(Thread[])

== ユーザー名検索 ==
user -> sm: 検索(userName)
sm -> sm: searchThreadUser(userName): Thread[]
sm -> th: スレッド取得(投稿者一致)
sm --> user: 検索結果(Thread[])

@enduml